sql:
SELECT t1.name, count(*)
FROM
site as s,
so_user as u1,
question as q1,
answer as a1,
tag as t1,
tag_question as tq1
WHERE
q1.owner_user_id = u1.id
AND a1.question_id = q1.id
AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id
AND s.site_id = q1.site_id
AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
AND s.site_id = t1.site_id
AND q1.id = tq1.question_id
AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
AND (s.site_name in ('askubuntu','math'))
AND (t1.name in ('elementary-number-theory','probability','proof-writing','unity'))
AND (q1.favorite_count >= 0)
AND (q1.favorite_count <= 1)
AND (u1.downvotes >= 10)
AND (u1.downvotes <= 100000)
GROUP BY t1.name;

FROM
site as s,
so_user as u1,
question as q1,

account as acc

s.site_id = q1.site_id

AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id

AND q1.id = tq1.question_id
AND q1.id = a1.question_id
AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id
AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
AND b.user_id = u1.id
AND acc.id = u1.account_id
AND (s.site_name in ('android','gamedev','judaism','rpg','webmasters'))

sql:
SELECT acc.location, count(*)
FROM
site as s,
so_user as u1,
question as q1,
answer as a1,
tag as t1,
tag_question as tq1,
badge as b,
account as acc
WHERE
s.site_id = q1.site_id
AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
AND s.site_id = t1.site_id
AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
AND s.site_id = b.site_id
AND q1.id = tq1.question_id
AND q1.id = a1.question_id
AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id
AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
AND b.user_id = u1.id
AND acc.id = u1.account_id
AND (s.site_name in ('stackoverflow','superuser'))
AND (t1.name in ('command-line','database','hibernate','java-8','qt'))
AND (q1.score >= 10)
AND (q1.score <= 1000)
AND (u1.downvotes >= 0)
AND (u1.downvotes <= 10)
AND (b.name in ('Autobiographer','Caucus','Commentator','Custodian','Informed','Nice Answer','Peer Pressure','Scholar','Self-Learner'))
GROUP BY acc.location
ORDER BY COUNT(*)
DESC
LIMIT 100;

SELECT acc.location, count(*)
FROM
site as s,
so_user as u1,
question as q1,
answer as a1,

tag_question as tq1,
badge as b,
account as acc
WHERE

AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id

AND b.user_id = u1.id

SELECT acc.location, count(*)
FROM
site as s,
so_user as u1,
question as q1,
answer as a1,
tag as t1,
tag_question as tq1,
badge as b,
account as acc
WHERE
s.site_id = q1.site_id
AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
AND s.site_id = t1.site_id
AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
AND s.site_id = b.site_id
AND q1.id = tq1.question_id
AND q1.id = a1.question_id
AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id
AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
AND b.user_id = u1.id
AND acc.id = u1.account_id
AND (s.site_name in ('android','gaming','money','sharepoint'))
AND (t1.name in ('development','investing','javascript','sharepoint-online','sharepoint-server','united-states','web-part'))
AND (q1.view_count >= 10)
AND (q1.view_count <= 1000)
AND (u1.reputation >= 10)
AND (u1.reputation <= 100000)
AND (b.name in ('Caucus','Constituent','Necromancer','Nice Answer','Tumbleweed'))
GROUP BY acc.location
ORDER BY COUNT(*)
DESC
LIMIT 100;

sql:
SELECT acc.location, count(*)
FROM
site as s,
so_user as u1,
question as q1,
answer as a1,
tag as t1,
tag_question as tq1,
badge as b,
account as acc
WHERE
s.site_id = q1.site_id
AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
AND s.site_id = t1.site_id
AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
AND s.site_id = b.site_id
AND q1.id = tq1.question_id
AND q1.id = a1.question_id
AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id
AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
AND b.user_id = u1.id
AND acc.id = u1.account_id
AND (s.site_name in ('askubuntu'))
AND (t1.name in ('13.04','17.10','cron','dependencies','ethernet','filesystem','juju','password','power-management','software-recommendation','uninstall','windows-7'))
AND (q1.view_count >= 10)
AND (q1.view_count <= 1000)
AND (u1.reputation >= 0)
AND (u1.reputation <= 100)
AND (b.name in ('Citizen Patrol','Commentator','Custodian','Famous Question','Promoter','Revival','Self-Learner'))
GROUP BY acc.location
ORDER BY COUNT(*)
DESC
LIMIT 100;

FROM

question as q,

AND (s.site_name in ('stackoverflow'))

sql:
SELECT acc.location, count(*)
FROM
site as s,
so_user as u1,
question as q1,
answer as a1,
tag as t1,
tag_question as tq1,
badge as b,
account as acc
WHERE
s.site_id = q1.site_id
AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
AND s.site_id = t1.site_id
AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
AND s.site_id = b.site_id
AND q1.id = tq1.question_id
AND q1.id = a1.question_id
AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id
AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
AND b.user_id = u1.id
AND acc.id = u1.account_id
AND (s.site_name in ('chemistry','mathematica'))
AND (t1.name in ('calculus-and-analysis','differential-equations','inorganic-chemistry','physical-chemistry'))
AND (q1.view_count >= 0)
AND (q1.view_count <= 100)
AND (u1.downvotes >= 0)
AND (u1.downvotes <= 1)
AND (b.name in ('Caucus','Citizen Patrol','Critic','Curious','Custodian','Enlightened','Famous Question','Good Question','Necromancer','Revival','Tumbleweed'))
GROUP BY acc.location
ORDER BY COUNT(*)
DESC
LIMIT 100;

FROM
site as s,
so_user as u1,
question as q1,
answer as a1,
tag as t1,
tag_question as tq1,
badge as b,
account as acc
WHERE
s.site_id = q1.site_id
AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
AND s.site_id = t1.site_id
AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
AND s.site_id = b.site_id
AND q1.id = tq1.question_id
AND q1.id = a1.question_id
AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id
AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
AND b.user_id = u1.id
AND acc.id = u1.account_id
AND (s.site_name in ('askubuntu','math'))
AND (t1.name in ('book-recommendation','gparted','order-theory'))
AND (q1.view_count >= 100)
AND (q1.view_count <= 100000)
AND (u1.upvotes >= 10)
AND (u1.upvotes <= 1000000)
AND (b.name in ('Altruist','Benefactor','Electorate','Fanatic','Generalist','Quorum','Self-Learner','Steward','Suffrage','Taxonomist','Vox Populi'))
GROUP BY acc.location
ORDER BY COUNT(*)
DESC
LIMIT 100;

sql:
SELECT acc.location, count(*)
FROM
site as s,
so_user as u1,
question as q1,
answer as a1,
tag as t1,
tag_question as tq1,
badge as b,
account as acc
WHERE
s.site_id = q1.site_id
AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
AND s.site_id = t1.site_id
AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
AND s.site_id = b.site_id
AND q1.id = tq1.question_id
AND q1.id = a1.question_id
AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id
AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
AND b.user_id = u1.id
AND acc.id = u1.account_id
AND (s.site_name in ('askubuntu','math'))
AND (t1.name in ('banach-spaces','grub2','hilbert-spaces','keyboard'))
AND (q1.favorite_count >= 0)
AND (q1.favorite_count <= 1)
AND (u1.upvotes >= 1)
AND (u1.upvotes <= 100)
AND (b.name in ('Enthusiast','Favorite Question'))
GROUP BY acc.location
ORDER BY COUNT(*)
DESC
LIMIT 100;
